def formula_2012_01_01(foyer_fiscal, period, parameters):

    t1 = ((f7wt * f7ws + f7wq + f7wf) > 0) * 1
    t2 = ((f7wc * f7wb + f7wa) > 0) * 1
    t3 = ((f7vg * f7vf + f7ve) > 0) * 1

    bouquet = ((t1 + t2 + t3 + t4 + t5 + t6) > 1) * (f7wh == 1)
    return bouquet
